    "patch_code": "Node processFunctionNode(FunctionNode functionNode) throws ParseError {\n  String nameString = functionNode.getName().getString();\n  if (nameString.length() == 0 && !functionNode.hasLexicalDeclarator() ) {\n       throw new ParseError(\"Unnamed function found.\");\n  }\n  return super.processFunctionNode(functionNode);\n}",
